	<h1 class="title">商业剪报：中产阶级财富流失，美国变穷了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1065/small/1065.jpg?1414574279" alt="">
