				<span class="name">李会娜 黄俊杰</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-07-28 10:25:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/1626/medium/1626.jpg?1436644946" alt="" />			
